txt.en: White Hand Orcs rush toward the overturned cart ready to attack.\n\nDefeat the White Hand attackers.
The road from Edoras to Aldburg sees much traffic, which makes it an attractive place for Orcs to attack.\n\nYou should be wary as you journey to Aldburg and deal with any threats as they arise.
This Orc-attack has been quelled, but it is only a matter of time before another one occurs. Nevertheless, you have made travel somewhat safer between Aldburg and Edoras.
